      "complete": "âœ… Standard setup complete! You have:\n   â€¢ Complete linting & formatting\n   â€¢ Comprehensive testing (unit + E2E)\n   â€¢ AI-powered test generation\n   â€¢ Performance monitoring\n   â€¢ CI/CD automation\n\nğŸ’¡ Run './auto-setup.sh --enterprise' for compliance tools"
    },
    "enterprise": {
      "start": "ğŸš€ Setting up AI-SDLC Framework - Enterprise Mode\n   ğŸ¢ Full enterprise features + compliance tools",
      "complete": "âœ… Enterprise setup complete! You have:\n   â€¢ All standard features\n   â€¢ Security scanning & compliance\n   â€¢ MCP server integration\n   â€¢ PostgreSQL automation\n   â€¢ MS Teams notifications\n   â€¢ FCRA compliance tools\n\nğŸ‰ Ready for enterprise development!"
